Constructor Detail

JsonWebEncryptionCryptoContext.RsaOaepCryptoContext

public JsonWebEncryptionCryptoContext.RsaOaepCryptoContext(PrivateKey privateKey,
                                                           PublicKey publicKey)

Create a new RSA crypto context for encrypt/decrypt using the provided public and private keys. All other operations are unsupported.

If there is no private key decryption is unsupported.

If there is no public key encryption is unsupported.

Parameters:
privateKey - the private key. May be null.
publicKey - the public key. May be null.
